// note-point:-
// Array-declaration:
// as toh jab Array-declare hota hai then mtlb vaha phle ek single-container allocate hota hai and uska naam given k equal hota hai and then uss single-bade-parent container meh chote-chote container allocate hoteh hai and unn containers ka naam hota hai name[0] , name[1] etc..etc.. toh mtlb apn unko unke naam se access kr skteh hai..
// and toh memory ki terms meh boleh toh as toh jab apn koi bhi vector-container declare krteh hai then vaha phle ek-single-parent-container allocate hota hai and usmeh phir sub-vector-or-scalar-containers allocate hoteh hai. and enn parent and parent-meh-Sub-containers k bhi naam hoteh hai. jaise array meh provided-name parent-container ko mil jata hai and sub-containers ki naming yeh essi hoti hai:- arrayname[0] , arrayname[1] ...etc.etc..  and jaise "classes" k liyeh toh declaration meh provided-name toh parent-container ka name hota hai and baki-sub-containers ka name toh jo apn class-design-defination meh provide krteh hai vohi hi hota hai.
